snippet.title: Police Bodycam Footage of Amber Heard & Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
This is an enhanced version of the bodycam footage from the Los Angeles Police Department filmed on May 2016.

Enhancements
1.Increased audio of Amber Heard. 
2. Fixed Audio Spikes.
3. Color Correction.

Amber Heard alleges that Johnny Depp hurled a phone at her face and trashed the penthouse kitchen during the notorious 2016 kerfuffle.

Depp's lawyers claim the depictions of damage – including broken candelabras, glass strewn on the floor, and red wine splashed on the walls as well as carpets – are completely and utterly false.
